Chadbourne & Parke Opens Istanbul Office, Appoints Ayse Yuksel

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-09-07T14:53:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/chadbourne-parke-opens-istanbul-office-appoints-ayse-yuksel.html
Chadbourne & Parke LLP, a New York-
based  law firm , opened an Istanbul office to focus on mergers
and acquisitions, private equity, capital markets and corporate
finance.  The firm appointed Ayse Yuksel as managing partner to lead
attorneys transferred from its New York and Dubai offices, the
firm said in an e-mailed  statement . The firm will work with
Cigdemtekin Sahbaz Attorney Partnership, a local law firm, to
provide Turkish legal advice to its clients.  Chadbourne will also offer tax services in  Turkey  through
another partner, Taylan Baykut, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net . 